<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.9">
<l>kūṭṭutiniṉ kuraikaḻalka ḷimaiyōrun toḻāvakai cey</l>
<l>tāṭṭutinī yaravaṇaiyā yaṭiyēṉu maḵtaṟivaṉ</l>
<l>vēṭkaiyellām viṭutteṉaiyuṉ ṟiruvaṭiyē cumantuḻala</l>
<l>kūṭṭariya tiruvaṭikkaḷ kūṭṭiṉaināṉ kaṇṭēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You would unite even the unblinking one with your [feet with] noisy anklets, you would make</l>
<l>[them] dance, acting in a way they do not worship, you on the serpert bed. I, [your] servant know that.</l>
<l>Making [me] let go of all desire I have seen you who united me</l>
<l>with [your] sacred feet difficult to unite with so that I roam burdened with your sacred feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
